CONTROLS

fly forward with spacebar and backward with backspace

strafe with the arrow keys
look with WASD or left click drag
if you get holonomy'd, you can twist with Q and E

X goes towards orthographic camera (everything is the same size no matter how far it is away)
Z goes towards perspective camera (normal)

Y/H, U/J, I/K, O/L, P/;, [/' are funny looking shear transformations

right click switches between distance view mode and normal (color) mode